---
title: Asian Beef & Sesame Garlic Rice Bowl with Japanese Mayo
description: Inject your night with a burst of flavours by combining gently marinated, bite-sized beef with aromatic garlic rice.  Top this baby off with a sesame fried egg and a drizzle of Japanese mayo for a dish that’ll have you salivating long before you plate up.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/asian-beef-sesame-garlic-rice-bowl-3a224bb4.jpg
